OL,5,CCourt hears
OL,7,FLiability is "no longer an issue" in
OL,8,Fclaims by thousands of officers and
OL,9,Fcivilian staff over a major PSNI data
OL,10,Fbreach, the High Court heard today.
OL,12,FA mediation process will now to be
OL,13,Fcarried out in a bid to agree on the
OL,14,Fpotential level of damages for the
OL,15,Fgroup action.
OL,17,FIn August last year personal
OL,18,Finformation on all serving police
OL,19,Fofficers and support workers was
OL,20,Fmistakenly published in response to a
OL,21,FFreedom of Information request.
