OL,7,FDetails released included the surname
OL,8,Fand first initial of every employee,
OL,9,Ftheir rank or grade, and the
OL,10,Fdepartment in which they work. Home
OL,11,Faddresses were not revealed.
OL,13,FWithin days of the leak it was
OL,14,Fconfirmed that dissident republicans
OL,15,Fhad accessed the information.
OL,17,FIt has been reported that the data
OL,18,Fbreach could cost the PSNI #240million
OL,19,Fin security and compensation payouts.
