OL,3,CLiability 'no longer an issue' in
OL,4,Cclaims over PSNI data breach, High
OL,5,CCourt hears
OL,7,FUp to 7,000 officers and civilian
OL,8,Fworkers are suing the force, with a
OL,9,Fgroup litigation order made and test
OL,10,Fcases identified as part of efforts to
OL,11,Fmanage the scale of lawsuits.
OL,13,FThe plaintiffs have brought claims for
OL,14,Fnegligence and breaches of data
OL,15,Fprotection and privacy.
OL,17,FIn court today, counsel for the PSNI,
OL,18,FNicolas Hanna KC, disclosed:
OL,19,F"Liability is no longer an issue, it's
OL,20,F(now) a matter of causation and
OL,21,Fdamages."
