OL,7,FMr Justice Colton was told both sides
OL,8,Fare set to begin mediation aimed at
OL,9,Fstreamlining the remaining issues.
OL,11,FThat process will involve trying to
OL,12,Fidentify a level of damages to put to
OL,13,Fthe plaintiffs as a "universal offer".
OL,15,F"Nobody would be bound to take it, but
OL,16,Fif the issues are properly explored in
OL,17,Fmediation it offers the best prospect
OL,18,Fof finding a figure (to recommend),"
OL,19,FMr Hanna said.
