OL,7,F"The objective is to try to get as
OL,8,Fmany cases resolved as soon as
OL,9,Fpossible, leaving a core which would
OL,10,Frequire more attention."
OL,12,FThree legal firms have been appointed
OL,13,Fas management solicitors representing
OL,14,Fmore than 6,000 of the police officers
OL,15,Fand staff taking the lawsuits.
OL,17,FTheir barristers, David Dunlop KC and
OL,18,FPeter Girvan, confirmed agreement to
OL,19,Fthe proposed mediation.
